summary: It\'s Custom Skyrim Launcher (CSL), for people, which have problems with their SkyrimLauncher.exe
descriptionHtml:
Custom The Elder Scrolls V : Skyrim Launcher

/////////////////////////   
v 0.1 alpha by PooSheQ
/////////////////////////   				
	    
1.How to install                            
2.Compatibility                             
3.Known bugs                                
4.Troubleshooting                           
                                            
/////////////////////////   					    
1.  How to install                          
					    					    
Just unzip where do you want                
And run Custom Skyrim Launcher.exe          
					    
/////////////////////////   					    
2.  Compatibility                           
					                                              
Checked on TESV.exe 1.7.7.0 version         
Used Skyrim Nexus Mod Manager version 0.19  
(After rename CSL.exe to SkyrimLauncher.exe
And put into Skyrim main folder )           					    

/////////////////////////   					    
3. Known bugs                               
					   					    
1.                                          
After deleting csl.ini, CSL.exe still thinks
that csl.ini exists                         					   
/////////////////////////                                            
4. Troubleshooting                          					 
                                            
1.Known bug                                 
Change directory of CSL.exe to other        
					    					    
If you see any bugs, e-mail me:             
k.dymecki1@gmail.com
